</div>
<div class="cnn_stryscbx3">
<a href="/2013/10/12/us/redskins-controversy/index.html?iid=article_sidebar"><img src="http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnn/dam/assets/140108092455-01-redskins-video-tease.jpg" alt="" border="0" height="68" width="120"/></a>
